dc_description_s: This data set is a polygon region features shapefile representing Wisconsin DNR Bear Management Zones as region features. Bear Management Zones indicate the areas with various bear hunting regulations throughout Wisconsin. Hunting regulations may vary between and within zones. Users should consult the most rcent Hunting Regulations Handbook to determine which regulations apply to which zones, or portions of zones. The current version of Bear Management Zone boundaries reflects updates made through October, 2008.
